metadata.name: Burger
metadata.description:
This 3D burger is designed for those with an unceasing hunger for burgers. It is uniquely designed to provide you with a vicarious pleasure to palpably experience different layers of a burger in virtual world.

The idea behind this work is that you can materialize a work of art "a burger" from papers and colors only with a snap of your fingers.

I called this work "col-burger" since it is made of color pencils. 

Hope this work is satisfying enough to catch your interest and attention.

Thank you for your time reading this;
Faranak Sattar
